      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"the world doesn't need you\" part is what sticks with me. It's like, if there’s no impact, then what’s the point of the struggle? The loneliness and the effort to keep going just feels like I'm fighting to maintain something that doesn't actually matter to anyone. It feels more like a burden than anything else.",
